{"tid":1977650,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"議員斥藉抗疫新例打壓異己","createTime":"2020-04-18T06:16:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T07:34:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"06caec3d45065702a53eae4d73dab1f55b6550b3","tid":1977650,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T06:16:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200418/2TEKNXYXDKOS5JVI3CDOUY5LMM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200418%2F2TEKNXYXDKOS5JVI3CDOUY5LMM%2F&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppegAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=4d20ec8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200418%2F2TEKNXYXDKOS5JVI3CDOUY5LMM%2F&h=9a1c5709\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200418/2TEKNXYXDKOS5JVI3CDOUY5LMM/</a><br />\n<br />\n議員斥藉抗疫新例打壓異己<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200418/large/1587141529_d4d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200418%2Flarge%2F1587141529_d4d4.jpg&h=a866f5b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方昨在酒吧取走CCTV硬碟機。司徒韋桐攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府上月底實施禁聚令以來，「黃店」食肆屢被警方及食環人員巡查，上月底悼念8.31活動的巿民亦被警方以疑超過四人聚集為藉口截查，外界質疑當局藉抗疫規例乘機打壓異己。民主黨立法會議員鄺俊宇昨在立法會財委會審議「抗疫基金2.0」撥款時，質問當局是否「厚此薄彼」拒向黃店批出資助，政務司司長張建宗聲稱，抗疫基金不分顏色，無政治掛帥。<br />\n<br />\n禁聚令3月29日起生效，黃店如基隆茶餐廳、光榮冰室、龍門冰室、大渣哥茶記等屢遭警方及食環署人員以接獲投訴為由「踩場」，在繁忙時段逐張餐桌拉尺量度距離有否違規，每每擾攘多時，有黃店負責人指連日來已數不到被巡查多少次。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府避答黃店違規會否失資助<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：青年貼諷習近平文宣 警爆粗辱罵<br />\n<br />\n鄺俊宇指，多間黃店近日被有關部門針對，又有傳言指違例食店不能領取抗疫資助，要求局方澄清，他認為目前社會萬眾一心抗疫，不應分政見而厚此薄彼，又斥警方連番針對黃店做法「小學雞」。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗辯稱：「防疫基金無分顏色，乜都冇嘅，我哋完全係實事求是，冇政治掛帥，真係為香港做事。」他更替曾譴責他的警隊開脫，指同事不會挑起事端，亦不會自找麻煩，有需要就會執法或巡查，籲大家不要想太多、或演繹得太過份。至於食店違規會否不獲發津貼，食物及衞生局局長陳肇始僅指基金派發時有不同資料考慮。<br />\n<br />\n■記者張珮琪"},{"pid":"855ba67404e9d7bd9f27aecbc4fc667992df896a","tid":1977650,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200418/large/1587141530_0e44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200418%2Flarge%2F1587141530_0e44.jpg&h=5e1f1c81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警務人員子女關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1870807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1870807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}